Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_s2m_port::_ctl

These registers contain control for access from SLI to a MAC port. Indexed by SLI_PORT_E. Write operations to these registers are not ordered with write/read operations to the MAC memory space. To ensure that a write operation has completed, read the register before making an access (i.e. MAC memory space) that requires the value of this register to be updated.
